name: The Champion
description: There's no one like this one on the ring anymore. Unyielding, Stiff-necked, Daredevil SOB. They left a promising career as mage, just to join this...blood sports. Orcs, Mermans, Efreets, Centaurs, all kind of terrifying creatures join the tournament. But they all fear the same monster, they all fear the champion...
